                    <!-- Text -->
                    <p>At Hiramani Memorial Hospital, we’ve built every corner of our facility with your safety and comfort in mind. Here’s what makes us unique:</p>

                    <p><b>Smart Design for Safer Care</b></p>

                    <ol>
                        <li><b>Separate Entries:</b> No crowded hallways! We use multiple entry points to keep patient flows organized and minimize contact between visitors, outpatients, and emergency cases.</li>

                        <li><b>Friendly Help Desks:</b> Our reception isn’t just a counter—it’s a help hub. From insurance paperwork to guiding you to the right department, we’re here to simplify your experience.</li>

                        <li><b>Green Practices:</b> Our in-house ETP and STP plants ensure wastewater is treated responsibly, keeping our community and environment clean.</li>

                        <li><b>Infection Control:</b> Every detail matters. Sterile corridors connect our Central Sterile Services Department (CSSD) to OTs, and unidirectional pathways in wards, ICU, and OTs ensure clean and contaminated areas never cross paths.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <p><b>Surgery Done Right</b></p>

                    <ol>
                        <li><b>Advanced Operating Theaters:</b> Airflow systems that keep the OT contaminant-free.</li>

                        <li>Antibacterial walls, touch-free automatic doors, and ultra-bright surgical lights for precision.</li>

                        <li>Special pass-through boxes and fire-safe systems for safe instrument and organ transfers.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <p><b>ICU: Where Technology Meets Compassion</b></p>

                    <ol>
                        <li><b>Smart ICU Beds:</b>Dialysis-ready beds with protective barriers to curb infections.</li>

                        <li>Cutting-edge monitors (Nihon Kohden) track lung pressure, energy needs, and more.</li>

                        <li>ECMO life support and sunny, naturally lit beds to aid recovery.</li>

                        <li><b>Isolation ICU:</b>A dedicated 5-bed unit with negative pressure to safely treat infectious cases.</li>

                        <li><b>BMT Unit:</b>Positive pressure rooms wrapped in antimicrobial Bioclad walls—first in the region!</li>
                    </ol>


                    <p><b>Recovery Made Easy</b></p>

                    <ol>
                        <li><b>Pre-Op Prep:</b> A calm, dedicated space to get you ready for surgery.</li>

                        <li><b>Post-Op Care:</b> Bright recovery bays with round-the-clock monitoring to ensure you wake up safely.</li>
